<div class="title">In the Eye of the Mind</div>
<div class="substance">Valerian  & Amphetamines (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Buddha&Exact=1">Buddha</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Buddha. "In the Eye of the Mind: An Experience with Valerian  & Amphetamines (Adderall) (exp19434)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. May 27, 2006. erowid.org/exp/19434</div>

<br/>



